Package: TTAT
Title: Tip Trait Association Test
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Leke",
           family = "Lyu",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "lekelyu@uga.edu",
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: This R package provides analytical methods to decide if the association between tips and characters is significant. By traversing the whole tree, the test would highlight all the subclades in which tips and characters are significantly associated.
